
/// Everything that appears on a line that starts with three slashes
/// is treated as a comment, and ignored.
/ Also, text within paired slashes like this is ignored. /

Fred told Mary a secret. John went into a restaurant. @

/// The special character '@' terminates the parse. Everything following
/// it is ignored. A '.' is parsed as the symbol *full-stop*. Two
/// carriage returns in a row is parsed as the symbol *paragraph*
